msgid "Access Control"
msgstr "上网控制"

msgid ""
"Access Control allows you to manage Internet access for specific local hosts."
"<br/> Each rule defines a device to block from having Internet access. The "
"rules may be active permanently or during certain times of the day.<br/> The "
"rules may also be restricted to specific days of the week.<br/> Any device "
"that is blocked may obtain a ticket suspending the restriction for a "
"specified time."
msgstr ""
"上网控制可以帮助您管理局域网中特定设备的 Internet 访问权限。<br/>"
"每条规则可以限制某个设备在特定时间段内无法上网，限制规则可以永久生效或在每天的特定时间生效。<br/>"
"规则还可以限定只在一周内的某些天生效。<br/>"
"任何当前被禁网的设备可以获取“临时上网卡（Ticket）”以在特定时间内临时恢复上网。"

